preference.name: TC_reactive_logging_file_delete
preference.preference_description: The PJL and JNL files will be removed from the temporary directory. This preference is only meant for reactive logging. Valid values are: * true: Deletes the PJL and JNL files from the temporary directory. * false: Does not delete the PJL and JNL file from the temporary directory.
